metadata.name: 'LIL TUNG$TY PICKLE$
metadata.description:

*All the details of this call can't be disclosed due to HIPAA regulations. But at the end of the call, something special happened.*
 
At the end of the call, Brian gave Dr. $uss a custom, right facing, $uss af, 1/1 that was held back from the OG Nickelodeon collection. CEO B-Money informed Dr. $ that this 1/1s name was TUNG$TY PICKLE$, cousin of Tommy Pickles, ofc. 'Lil T lived right across the street from Nickelodeon Studios in the $uburb of Den$elodeon $tudios.

Later that evening, The CEO of Hollywood, Brian Robbins, called Dr. $ and advised him to auction the piece off. He stated that 69% of proceeds must go to the chads and chadettes of the @TungstenDAO

Brian is unbelievable proud of his CC0, right facing, 'LIL TUNG$TY PICKLE$.
